# Modern Logger

A high-performance, flexible logging system with file, console, and GUI output options designed for modern Python applications.

## ‚ú® Features

- **üöÄ High Performance**: Optimized for minimal overhead and efficient memory usage
- **üéØ Multiple Output Options**: Log to files, console, GUI, or any combination
- **üìÅ Smart File Logging**: Automatic file creation and intelligent directory handling  
- **üé® Colorful Console**: Rich console output with customizable colors using colorama
- **üñ•Ô∏è Modern GUI (PySide6)**: Advanced Qt-based interface with progress indicators, scroll management, and real-time updates
- **üîÄ Multi-Logger**: Send logs to multiple destinations simultaneously with intelligent routing
- **‚ö° Lazy Loading**: PySide6 only imported when GUI functionality is requested
- **üì¶ Optional Dependencies**: Full CLI functionality without installing GUI dependencies (PySide6)
- **üìä Advanced Export**: Export logs in multiple formats (LOG, CSV, XML, JSON) with filtering and metadata
- **üßµ Thread-Safe**: Fully thread-safe for multithreaded applications
- **üíæ Memory Management**: Automatic memory management for long-running applications

